{"tid":448441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領取綜援人士可獲十元減廢津貼","createTime":"2017-10-26T08:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T09:00:44.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24cd619c46aac2444b1a63d67fd3f182fe075bc3","tid":448441,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:23:57.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】垃圾徵費最快後年實施，環境局局長黃錦星表示諮詢業界意見後，決定擴大按袋收費至私營的垃圾收集商，在優化計劃下，預計有八成固體廢物以按袋收費形式處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府原本建議有三年的過渡安排，即部分住宅大廈「按桶」徵費，再由住戶攤分費用。當局徵詢業界意見後決定取消有關安排，亦會為領取綜援人士提供每月十元的減廢津貼，紓緩他們的經濟負擔。"},{"pid":"3d43e5b75c4b2343d2c87c642aaaf2ec730cbcfd","tid":448441,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f979aecd508532217b31f04b9a45276761af578","tid":448441,"uid":22974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa36d21d7c43f81ca28a635763a821a2a560a6e","tid":448441,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌，嫌香港人未夠苦。又開多辦收錢</blockquote><br />\n當初垃圾焚化搞得掂，根本就冇呢種煩惱。"},{"pid":"e6690c03af2b7c06b992acd172382d5867cd462f","tid":448441,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>減完佢哋可以同人講自己冇咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎綜援有咩咁廢呀屌你老母肥絲大只"},{"pid":"5c6c3f78136a93e415e2ac20c8450b34f18c9344","tid":448441,"uid":49004,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:56:45.000Z","msg":"點解唔津貼佢地買dom<br />\n源頭減廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c801accb61903b099c83e5412273828b2b0d44cd","tid":448441,"uid":32841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔津貼佢地買dom<br />\n源頭減廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"